NK037(ji)020:0: rnam sras yang gsang phyag mtshan bzhi pa'i sgrub thabs rjes gnang dang bcas pa bzhugs /
NK037(ji)020:2: rin chen mang sprul rnam thos sras //
NK037(ji)020:3: gnod sbyin dbang po der btud nas //
NK037(ji)020:4: gang gi sgrub thabs rjes gnang gi //
NK037(ji)020:5: cho ga mdo tsam gsal bar bya //
NK037(ji)020:6: 'dir mdung dmar can yang gsang phyag mtshan bzhi pa'i
NK037(ji)020:7: sgrub thabs rjes gnang gi cho ga thams cad nang
NK037(ji)020:8: sgrub rta sngon can gyi cho ga shes nas 'jug
NK037(ji)020:9: par bya ste / de la sbyor ba yo byad kyi gshom /
NK037(ji)020:10: dngos gzhi sgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK037(ji)020:12: dang po yo byad bsham pa ni /
NK037(ji)020:13: sgrub pa'i skabs su man+dala gyi dbus su bla rdo'i
NK037(ji)020:14: gri snying 'jog par gsungs kyang rjes gnang tsam la
NK037(ji)020:15: rten gtor bkod pa sogs nang sgrub kyi skabs bzhin
NK037(ji)020:16: no // gnyis pa sgrub pa'i thabs ni /
NK037(ji)020:19: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs dang bcas pa /
NK037(ji)020:20: rdo rje'i sa gzhi la gnas shing ra bas bskor
NK037(ji)020:21: ba mtshan nyid thams cad rdzogs shing rgyan gyis brgyan
NK037(ji)020:22: pa'i lte bar / tsa las seng ge'i steng du
NK037(ji)020:23: rin po che'i khri pad zla nyi ma'i gdan la
NK037(ji)020:24: bee yig dmar po'i 'phro 'du las rgyal po chen
NK037(ji)020:25: po rnam thos sras sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig
NK037(ji)020:26: pa'i lte bar / phyag gnyis pa / spyan gnyis dmar la zlum pa /
NK037(ji)020:27: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)020:28: phyag g.yas stag gi rgyal mtshan dang mdung dmar phyar zhing /
NK037(ji)020:29: g.yon ne'u le dang lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)020:30: sku brjid pa'i cha lugs can dar gyi na bza' dang rdo rje'i mtshan pa'i bse khrab gsol ba /
NK037(ji)020:32: dbu la bse'i rmog zhu dar dmar gyi cod pan 'phur ba bcings pa /
NK037(ji)020:33: sku dang phyag mtshan las 'od zer dmar po lcags
NK037(ji)020:34: kyu lta bu 'phro bas 'gro ba thams cad dbang
NK037(ji)020:36: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u gi 'od zer las khro
NK037(ji)020:37: bo 'dod pa'i rgyal po byung ste rgyal po 'khor
NK037(ji)020:38: bcas spyan drangs par bsam zhing lcags kyu'i phyag rgya
NK037(ji)020:40: ri rgyal lhun po'i byang phyogs nas //
NK037(ji)020:41: rgyal po chen po rnams thos sras //
NK037(ji)020:42: sku mdog ye nas dmar gsal la //
NK037(ji)020:43: phyag g.yas rgyal mtshan mdung dmar thogs //
NK037(ji)020:44: phyag g.yon ne'u le lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK037(ji)020:45: bskal pa bzang po'i dus tsam na //
NK037(ji)020:46: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas kyang //
NK037(ji)020:47: da lta rgyal po'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK037(ji)020:48: gnod sbyin nor lha pho mo dang //
NK037(ji)020:49: klu chen brgyad po 'khor dang bcas //
NK037(ji)020:50: byang phyogs gnas na bzhugs pa rnams //
NK037(ji)020:52: ma h+aa yak+sha r+aa dza bee sh+ra ma na ya sa ma ya dzah zhes pas spyan drangs /
NK037(ji)020:53: cod pan gyi dbang bskur ba nas bzung /
NK037(ji)020:55: gtor ma 'bul ba sogs nas rjes chog gi bar nang sgrub rta sngon gyi skabs bzhin dang /
NK037(ji)020:56: gsum pa rjes gnang gi cho ga'ang lha'i mngon rtogs
NK037(ji)020:57: spo ba tsam las dbye ba med pas de ltar
NK037(ji)020:58: shes par bya'o // bsnyen sgrub las sbyor gyi man
NK037(ji)020:59: ngag zhib mo ni gter gzhung rtsa ba dang gnyags
NK037(ji)020:60: dbon chos rje'i yi ge la blta bar bya'o //
NK037(ji)020:61: 'di la yang gsang mkha' 'gro ltar sgrub pa zhes
NK037(ji)020:62: pa'i tha snyad ni sgrub pa'i skabs su thugs kar
NK037(ji)020:63: bee las rgyal po rang 'dra bskyed pa'i phyogs bzhir
NK037(ji)020:64: ma trag bzhi las mkha' 'gro ma bzhi bskyed bar
NK037(ji)020:66: rtsa ba'i 'khor du rta bdag brgyad dang /
NK037(ji)020:67: klu chen brgyad bskyed pa'ang gsungs shing /
NK037(ji)020:68: rjes gnang gi skabs 'dir gtso bo dang las mkhan te lha gnyis su bshad pa'ang 'dug mod /
NK037(ji)020:69: gzhung rtsa ba las gtso rkyang du gsungs pa ltar byas so //
NK037(ji)020:70: 'di dang mthun pa'i sgrub thabs chos dbang gi gter ma zhig kyang snang ngo //
NK037(ji)020:71: yang rat+na gling pa dang pad+ma gling pa'i gter ma'i phyag mtshan bzhi pa ni /
NK037(ji)020:72: gtso bo 'di dang mngon rtogs mtshungs pa la /
NK037(ji)020:73: rta bdag brgyad kyis bskor ba'i sgrub thabs spyi khog 'di dang mthun rung du yod kyang /
NK037(ji)020:74: rjes gnang gi cho ga ni tha dad pa'o //
NK037(ji)020:75: shes par 'dod na sgrub thabs dngos grub rol mtsho dang rjes gnang gter gzhung las shes par bya'o //
NK037(ji)020:76: rgyal chen phyi nang gsang ba yi //
NK037(ji)020:77: rnam 'gyur sgrub thabs mtha' med pa'i //
NK037(ji)020:78: snying po rdo rje 'dzin dbang gi //
NK037(ji)020:79: zhal lung ji bzhin nyung ngur dril //
NK037(ji)020:80: mdung dmar can yang gsang phyag mtshan bzhi pa'i sgrub
NK037(ji)020:81: thabs rjes gnang dang bcas pa'i le'u tshan gter chen
NK037(ji)020:82: 'gyur med rdo rje'i gsung sgrub thabs 'dod 'jo'i bum
